___SANDBOXED_JS_FOR_WEB_TEMPLATE___

/*
    Web Site Advantage: Rally Facebook Pixel [v1.0] 
    Facebook Checkout Code for Rally
    https://bigcommerce.websiteadvantage.com.au/tag-rocket/
    Copyright (C) 2022 Web Site Advantage
*/
const containerLabel = 'tag_rocket_rally_facebook';

// https://developers.google.com/tag-platform/tag-manager/templates/api
const logToConsole = require('logToConsole');
const createQueue = require('createQueue');
const callInWindow = require('callInWindow');
const aliasInWindow = require('aliasInWindow');
const copyFromWindow = require('copyFromWindow');
const copyFromDataLayer = require('copyFromDataLayer');
const setInWindow = require('setInWindow');
const injectScript = require('injectScript');
const makeInteger = require('makeInteger');
const templateStorage = require('templateStorage');

const log = function(text) {logToConsole(containerLabel + ': '+text , arguments);};
log('data =', data);

const rallyEvent = copyFromDataLayer('rally', 1);
log('rallyEvent =', rallyEvent);

const facebookIds = data.facebookIds.split(',');
log('Ids =', facebookIds);

// Utility function to use either fbq.queue[]
// (if the FB SDK hasn't loaded yet), or fbq.callMethod()
// if the SDK has loaded.
// https://github.com/facebookarchive/GoogleTagManager-WebTemplate-For-FacebookPixel/blob/main/template.tpl
const getFbq = () => {
    // Return the existing 'fbq' global method if available
    log('getFbq');
    let fbq = copyFromWindow('fbq');
  
    log('getFbq fbq',fbq);
    if (fbq) {
        return fbq;
    }

    // Initialize the 'fbq' global method to either use
    // fbq.callMethod or fbq.queue)
    setInWindow('fbq', function() {    
        const callMethod = copyFromWindow('fbq.callMethod.apply');
        if (callMethod) {           
            callInWindow('fbq.callMethod.apply', null, arguments); 
        } else {       
            callInWindow('fbq.queue.push', arguments);
        }
    });
    aliasInWindow('_fbq', 'fbq');

    // Create the fbq.queue
    createQueue('fbq.queue');
        
    // Return the global 'fbq' method, created above
    return copyFromWindow('fbq');
};

log('about to getFbq');
// Get reference to the global method
const fbq = getFbq();

log('fbq =', fbq);

if (!templateStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_config')) {
    templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_config','done');
    templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_init_options',{});
    templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_init_send',true);
    templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_pageview_send',true);

    // Automatic Configuration
    if (data.automaticConfiguration === false) {
        facebookIds.forEach(facebookId => {
            log('fbq set ' +facebookId);
            fbq('set', 'autoConfig', false, facebookId);
        });
    }

    // Consent
    const consent = 'off'; // off, grant or revoke

    if (consent != 'off') {
        log('consent ', consent);
        fbq('consent', consent);
    }


    // Data Processing Options - don't set if consent has been specifically granted
    if (consent != 'grant' && data.limitedDataUse === true) {
        log('fbq dataProcessingOptions');
        fbq('dataProcessingOptions',['LDU'],0,0);
    }
}

// send user data? we don't have it when the page loads!
// https://developers.facebook.com/docs/facebook-pixel/advanced/advanced-matching
// https://developers.facebook.com/ads/blog/post/v2/2017/11/28/event-tracking-with-multiple-pixels-tracksingle/
if (rallyEvent.name === 'customer' || rallyEvent.name === 'address') {
    if (data.advancedMatching === true) {
        const initOptions = templateStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_init_options');

        if (rallyEvent.email) initOptions.em = rallyEvent.email;
        if (rallyEvent.phone) initOptions.ph = rallyEvent.phone;
        if (rallyEvent.firstName) initOptions.fn = rallyEvent.firstName;
        if (rallyEvent.lastName) initOptions.ln = rallyEvent.lastName;
      
        if (rallyEvent.shipping) {
            if (rallyEvent.shipping.city) initOptions.ct = rallyEvent.shipping.city;
            if (rallyEvent.shipping.countryCode) initOptions.country = rallyEvent.shipping.countryCode;
            if (rallyEvent.shipping.province) initOptions.st = rallyEvent.shipping.province;
            if (rallyEvent.shipping.zip) initOptions.zp = rallyEvent.shipping.zip;
        }

        log('initOptions =', initOptions);

        templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_init_options',initOptions);
        templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_init_send',true);
    }
};

const sendInitIfRequired = () => {
    if (templateStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_init_send')) {

        const initOptions = templateStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_init_options');

        facebookIds.forEach(facebookId => {
            log('init', facebookId, initOptions);
            fbq('init', facebookId, initOptions);
        });
        templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_init_send',false);
    }
};

const productIdentifier = (product) => {
    switch(data.productIdentifier) {
        case "externalProductId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
        case "sku":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.sku;
        case "externalVariantId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalVariantId;
        default:
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
    }
}; 

const contentType = () => {
    switch(data.productIdentifier) {
        case "externalProductId":
            return 'product_group';
        case "sku":
        case "externalVariantId":
            return 'product';
        default:
            return 'product_group';
    }
};

if (rallyEvent.name === 'step') {
    if (templateStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_pageview_send')) {
        templateStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_pageview_send',false);

        // here so customer data events have already fired and populated the init options
        sendInitIfRequired();
        log('track PageView');
        fbq('track', 'PageView'); 
    }
}

// step 1 = checkout started
const processStep1 = () => { 
    const lineItems = rallyEvent.cart.lineItems;
    const contents = [];
    const content_ids = [];
    let item_cnt = 0;

    lineItems.forEach(function(item) {
        const id = productIdentifier(item).toString();
        content_ids.push(id);
        contents.push({
            "id": id,
            "quantity": item.quantity,
            "price": item.price,
            "title": item.title
        });
        item_cnt += makeInteger(item.quantity);
    });
    
    const eventData = {
        "content_name": "Rally Initiate Checkout",
        "content_ids": content_ids,
        "content_type": contentType(),
        "contents": contents,
        "value": rallyEvent.cart.total,
        "num_items": item_cnt,
        "currency": rallyEvent.cart.currency
    };

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.promo_code = rallyEvent.discountCodes;
    
    log('track InitiateCheckout', eventData);

    sendInitIfRequired();

    fbq('track', 'InitiateCheckout', eventData);
};

// step 2 = shipping filled in, on delivery page
const processStep2 = () => {
};

// step 3 = delivery filled in, on payment page
const processStep3 = () => { 
};

// step 4 = order complete
const processStep4 = () => { 
    const lineItems = rallyEvent.cart.lineItems;
    const contents = [];
    const content_ids = [];
    let item_cnt = 0;

    lineItems.forEach(function(item) {
        const id = productIdentifier(item).toString();
        content_ids.push(id);
        contents.push({
            "id": id,
            "quantity": item.quantity,
            "price": item.price,
            "title": item.title
            // vendor?
        });
        item_cnt += makeInteger(item.quantity);
    });
    if (content_ids.length > 0) {
        
        const eventData =  {
            "content_name": "Rally Purchase",
            "content_ids": content_ids,
            "content_type": contentType(),
            "contents": contents,
            "value": rallyEvent.cart.total,
            "num_items": item_cnt,
            "currency": rallyEvent.cart.currency
        };

        if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.promo_code = rallyEvent.discountCodes;
        
        log('track Purchase', eventData);

        sendInitIfRequired();
                
        fbq('track', 'Purchase', eventData);
    }
};

if (rallyEvent && rallyEvent.name === 'step' && rallyEvent.step) {
    switch(rallyEvent.step) {
        case 1:
            processStep1();
            break;
        case 2:
            processStep2();
            break;
        case 3:
            processStep3();
            break;
        case 4:
            processStep4();
            break;
    }
}

injectScript('https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js', data.gtmOnSuccess, data.gtmOnFailure, 'fbPixel');

___SANDBOXED_JS_FOR_WEB_TEMPLATE___

/*
    Web Site Advantage: Rally to GA3 dataLayer Events [v1.0] 
    Converts Rally datalayer events to GA3 dataLayer Events
    https://bigcommerce.websiteadvantage.com.au/tag-rocket/
    Copyright (C) 2022 Web Site Advantage
*/

// in the GA4 config set field ignore_referrer to true

const containerLabel = 'tag_rocket_rally_ga3';

// https://developers.google.com/tag-platform/tag-manager/templates/api
const logToConsole = require('logToConsole');
const createQueue = require('createQueue');
const copyFromDataLayer = require('copyFromDataLayer');

const log = function(text) {logToConsole(containerLabel + ': '+text , arguments);};
log('data =', data);

//const event = copyFromDataLayer('event');
const rallyEvent = copyFromDataLayer('rally', 1);
log('rallyEvent =', rallyEvent);

const dlPush = createQueue('dataLayer');

const productIdentifier = (product) => {
    switch(data.productIdentifier) {
        case "externalProductId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
        case "sku":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.sku;
        case "externalVariantId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalVariantId;
        default:
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
    }
}; 

// make items for the events
const createItems = (cart) => { 
    const lineItems = cart.lineItems;
    const items = [];

    lineItems.forEach(function(item) {
        const id = productIdentifier(item).toString();
        items.push({
            id: id,
            quantity: item.quantity,
            price: item.price,
            name: item.title,
            variant: item.externalVariantId.toString(),
        });
    });
    return items;
};

// step 1 = checkout started
const processStep1 = () => { 
    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ua/gtm/enhanced-ecommerce#checkout
    const eventData = {
        event: 'eec.checkout',
        ecommerce: {
            checkout: {
                currencyCode: rallyEvent.cart.currency,
                actionField: {step: 1}, 
                products: createItems(rallyEvent.cart)
            }
        }    
    };

    log('checkout', eventData);

    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

// step 2 = shipping filled in, on delivery page
const processStep2 = () => { 
    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ua/gtm/enhanced-ecommerce#checkout
    const eventData = {
        event: 'eec.checkout',
        ecommerce: {
            checkout: {
                currencyCode: rallyEvent.cart.currency,
                actionField: {step: 2}, 
                products: createItems(rallyEvent.cart)
            }
        }    
    };

    log('checkout', eventData);

    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

// step 3 = delivery filled in, on payment page
const processStep3 = () => { 
    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ua/gtm/enhanced-ecommerce#checkout
    const eventData = {
        event: 'eec.checkout',
        ecommerce: {
            checkout: {
                currencyCode: rallyEvent.cart.currency,
                actionField: {step: 3, option: rallyEvent.shippingMethod}, 
                products: createItems(rallyEvent.cart)
            }
        }    
    };

    log('checkout', eventData);

    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

// step 4 = order complete
const processStep4 = () => { 

    let eventData = {
        event: 'eec.checkout',
        ecommerce: {
            checkout: {
            currencyCode: rallyEvent.cart.currency,
            actionField: {step: 4, option: rallyEvent.cart.payment.type}, 
            products: createItems(rallyEvent.cart)
            }
        }    
    };

    log('eec.checkout', eventData);

    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);

    // purchase 
    let actionField = {
        id: rallyEvent.orderId, 
    //   affiliation: 'Online Store',
        revenue: rallyEvent.cart.total, 
        tax: rallyEvent.cart.tax,
        shipping: rallyEvent.cart.shipping || 0
    };

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) actionField.coupon = rallyEvent.discountCodes;

    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ua/gtm/enhanced-ecommerce#purchases
    eventData = {
        event: 'eec.purchase',
        ecommerce: {  
            currencyCode: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            purchase: {
                actionField: actionField,
                products: createItems(rallyEvent.cart)
            }
        }    
    };

    log('eec.purchase', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

if (rallyEvent && rallyEvent.name === 'step' && rallyEvent.step) {
    switch(rallyEvent.step) {
        case 1:
            processStep1();
            break;
        case 2:
            processStep2();
            break;
        case 3:
            processStep3();
            break;
        case 4:
            processStep4();
            break;
    }
}

data.gtmOnSuccess();

const containerLabel = 'tag_rocket_rally_gads';

log('data =', data);

//const event = copyFromDataLayer('event');
const rallyEvent = copyFromDataLayer('rally', 1);
log('rallyEvent =', rallyEvent);

const productIdentifier = (product) => {
    switch(data.productIdentifier) {
        case "externalProductId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
        case "sku":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.sku;
        case "externalVariantId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalVariantId;
        default:
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;

}; 

// make items for the events
const createItems = (cart) => { 
    const lineItems = cart.lineItems;

    lineItems.forEach(function(item) {

        items.push({
            id: id,
            quantity: item.quantity,
            price: item.price,
            google_business_vertical:'retail'
        });
    });
    return items;
};

// step 1 = checkout started
const processStep1 = () => { 
};

// step 2 = shipping filled in, on delivery page

};

// step 3 = delivery filled in, on payment page
const processStep3 = () => { 
};

// step 4 = order complete
const processStep4 = () => { 
    let eventData = {
        event: 'gads.purchase',
        googleads: {  
            transaction_id: rallyEvent.orderId,                             
            currency: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            items: createItems(rallyEvent.cart),
            value: rallyEvent.cart.total
            //discount
        }    
    };

    log('gads.purchase', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ googleads: null });  // Clear the previous googleads object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

if (rallyEvent && rallyEvent.name === 'step' && rallyEvent.step) {
    switch(rallyEvent.step) {
        case 1:
            processStep1();
            break;
        case 2:
            processStep2();
            break;
        case 3:
            processStep3();
            break;
        case 4:

            break;

}

/*
    Web Site Advantage: Rally dataLayer Events [v1.0] 
    Sends rally events to the dataLayer
    https://bigcommerce.websiteadvantage.com.au/tag-rocket/
    Copyright (C) 2022 Web Site Advantage
*/
const containerLabel = 'tag_rocket_rally';

// https://developers.google.com/tag-platform/tag-manager/templates/api
const logToConsole = require('logToConsole');
const createQueue = require('createQueue');
const callInWindow = require('callInWindow');
const copyFromDataLayer = require('copyFromDataLayer');
const localStorage = require('localStorage'); 
const templateStorage = require('templateStorage');

const log = function(text) {logToConsole(containerLabel + ': '+text , arguments);};
log('data =', data);

const dlPush = createQueue('dataLayer');

callInWindow('Rally.events.subscribe', 'customer.updated', (eventData) => {
    templateStorage.setItem('customer', eventData);
    const rallyEvent = {
        event: 'rally.customer.updated',
        rally: {
            name: 'customer',
            data: eventData
        }    
    };
    dlPush({rally: null});
    dlPush(rallyEvent);
});
callInWindow('Rally.events.subscribe', 'address.updated', (eventData) => {
    templateStorage.setItem('address', eventData);
    const rallyEvent = {
        event: 'rally.address.updated',
        rally: {
            name: 'address',
            data: eventData
        }    
    };
    dlPush({rally: null});
    dlPush(rallyEvent);
});

callInWindow('Rally.events.subscribe', 'discount.updated', (eventData) => {
    if (eventData && eventData.length > 0) {
        templateStorage.setItem('discountCodes', eventData
            .map(discount => discount.name)
            .join(', ')); 
    }
    else {
        templateStorage.removeItem('discountCodes');
    }
});

callInWindow('Rally.events.subscribe', 'shippingOptions.updated', (eventData) => {
    if (eventData && eventData.length > 0) {
        templateStorage.setItem('shippingMethod', eventData
            .filter(method => method.isSelected === true)
            .map(method => method.title)
            .join(', ')); 
    }
    else {
        templateStorage.removeItem('shippingMethod');
    }
});

const newStep = (step) => {
    log('newStep');
    if (localStorage) {
        const maxStep = localStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_step');
        if (maxStep && maxStep >= step) {
            log('newStep '+step+ ' is less than or equal to maxStep '+maxStep + ' so do nothing');
            return false;
        }
        else {
            log('newStep '+step+ ' is greater than maxStep '+maxStep + ' so process it');
            localStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_step', step);
            return true;
        }
    }
    return true;
};

const processStep = (step) => { 
    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ga4/ecommerce?client_type=gtm#begin_checkout   
    log('processStep '+step);
    const rallyEvent = {
        event: 'rally.step.'+step,
        rally: {
            name: 'step',
            step: step,
            cart: templateStorage.getItem('cartData'),
            discountCodes: templateStorage.getItem('discountCodes'),
            shippingMethod: templateStorage.getItem('shippingMethod'),
            customer: templateStorage.getItem('customer'),
            address: templateStorage.getItem('address')
        }    
    };

    const order = callInWindow('Rally.data.order.get');

    if (order) {
        rallyEvent.rally.orderId = order.id;
    }

    log('processStep '+step, rallyEvent);

    dlPush({rally: null});
    dlPush(rallyEvent);
};

const processSteps = (currentStep) => {
    log('processSteps to '+currentStep);

    if (currentStep >= 1 && newStep(1)) {
        log('calling processStep 1');
        processStep(1);
    }
    if (currentStep >= 2 && newStep(2)) {
        processStep(2);
    }
    if (currentStep >= 3 && newStep(3)) {
        processStep(3);
    }
    if (currentStep >= 4 && newStep(4)) {
        const order = callInWindow('Rally.data.order.get');

        if (order) {
            let lastOrderId = null;

            if (localStorage) {
                lastOrderId = localStorage.getItem(containerLabel+'_last');
            }

            if (order.id && order.id != lastOrderId) {  
                if (localStorage) {
                    localStorage.setItem(containerLabel+'_last', order.id);
                }
                processStep(4);
            }
        }
    }
    if (currentStep >= 4) {
        if (localStorage) {
            localStorage.removeItem(containerLabel+'_step');
        }
    }
}; 

const newHistoryState = copyFromDataLayer('gtm.newHistoryState', 1);
log('newHistoryState =', newHistoryState);

if (newHistoryState && newHistoryState.step && newHistoryState.step !== 1) { // a history event after a pageView and when each step is flagged
    processSteps(newHistoryState.step);  
}
else {
    // pageView
    
    callInWindow('Rally.events.subscribe', 'cart.initiated', (cartData) => {
        templateStorage.setItem('cartData', cartData);

        const page = callInWindow('Rally.data.page.get');

        if (page) {
            switch(page.type) {
                case 'checkout':    
                    processSteps(1);
                    break;
                case 'confirmation':      
                    processSteps(4);
                    break; 
            }
        }
    }); 
}

data.gtmOnSuccess();

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.ecommerce.coupon = rallyEvent.discountCodes;

    log('begin_checkout', eventData);

    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

// step 2 = shipping filled in, on delivery page
const processStep2 = () => { 
    // no official event. Use the same one as Tag Rocket
    const eventData = {
        event: 'add_customer_info',
        ecommerce: {  
            currency: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            items: createItems(rallyEvent.cart),
            value: rallyEvent.cart.total
        }    
    };

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.ecommerce.coupon = rallyEvent.discountCodes;

    log('add_customer_info', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

// step 3 = delivery filled in, on payment page
const processStep3 = () => { 
    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ga4/ecommerce?client_type=gtm#add_shipping_info
    const eventData = {
        event: 'add_shipping_info',
        ecommerce: {  
            currency: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            items: createItems(rallyEvent.cart),
            value: rallyEvent.cart.total,
            shipping_tier: rallyEvent.shippingMethod
        }    
    };

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.ecommerce.coupon = rallyEvent.discountCodes;

    log('add_shipping_info', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

// step 4 = order complete
const processStep4 = () => { 
          
    const items = createItems(rallyEvent.cart);

    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ga4/ecommerce?client_type=gtm#add_payment_info
    let eventData = {
        event: 'add_payment_info',
        ecommerce: {  
            currency: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            items: items,
            value: rallyEvent.cart.total,
            payment_type: rallyEvent.cart.payment.type
        }    
    };

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.ecommerce.coupon = rallyEvent.discountCodes;

    log('add_payment_info', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);

    // https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/ga4/ecommerce?client_type=gtm#purchase
    eventData = {
        event: 'purchase',
        ecommerce: {  
            transaction_id: rallyEvent.orderId, 
            currency: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            items: items,
            value: rallyEvent.cart.total,
            tax: rallyEvent.cart.tax,
            shipping: rallyEvent.cart.shipping || 0
        }    
    };

    if (rallyEvent.discountCodes) eventData.ecommerce.coupon = rallyEvent.discountCodes;

    log('purchase', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ ecommerce: null });  // Clear the previous ecommerce object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

if (rallyEvent && rallyEvent.name === 'step' && rallyEvent.step) {
    switch(rallyEvent.step) {
        case 1:
            processStep1();
            break;
        case 2:
            processStep2();
            break;
        case 3:
            processStep3();
            break;
        case 4:
            processStep4();
            break;
    }
}

data.gtmOnSuccess();

/*
    Web Site Advantage: Rally to Microsoft Ads dataLayer Events [v1.0] 
    Converts Rally datalayer events to Microsoft Ads dataLayer Events
    https://bigcommerce.websiteadvantage.com.au/tag-rocket/
    Copyright (C) 2022 Web Site Advantage
*/

// in the GA4 config set field ignore_referrer to true

const containerLabel = 'tag_rocket_rally_microsoft';

// https://developers.google.com/tag-platform/tag-manager/templates/api
const logToConsole = require('logToConsole');
const createQueue = require('createQueue');
const copyFromDataLayer = require('copyFromDataLayer');
const Math = require('Math');

const log = function(text) {logToConsole(containerLabel + ': '+text , arguments);};
log('data =', data);

//const event = copyFromDataLayer('event');
const rallyEvent = copyFromDataLayer('rally', 1);
log('rallyEvent =', rallyEvent);

const dlPush = createQueue('dataLayer');

const productIdentifier = (product) => {
    switch(data.productIdentifier) {
        case "externalProductId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
        case "sku":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.sku;
        case "externalVariantId":
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalVariantId;
        default:
            return data.productIdentifierPrefix+product.externalProductId;
    }
}; 
const roundTo = (number,places) => { 
    if(!number)return number;
    if(!places)places=0;
    const multiplier=Math.pow(10,places);
    const epsilon=0.00000000000000002220446049250313;
    return Math.round((number+epsilon)*multiplier)/multiplier;
};


// make items for the events
const createItems = (cart) => { 
    const lineItems = cart.lineItems;
    const items = [];

    lineItems.forEach(function(item) {
        const id = productIdentifier(item).toString();
        items.push({
            id: id,
            quantity: item.quantity,
            price: roundTo(item.price,3),
            name: item.title,
            variant: item.externalVariantId.toString()
        });
    });
    return items;
};

const createProductIds = (cart) => { 
    const lineItems = cart.lineItems;
    const productIds = [];

    lineItems.forEach(function(item) {
        const id = productIdentifier(item).toString();
        productIds.push(id);
    });
    return productIds;
};

// step 1 = checkout started
const processStep1 = () => { 
};

// step 2 = shipping filled in, on delivery page
const processStep2 = () => { 
};

// step 3 = delivery filled in, on payment page
const processStep3 = () => { 
};

// step 4 = order complete
const processStep4 = () => { 
    let eventData = {
        event: 'mads.purchase',
        microsoftads: {  
            transaction_id: rallyEvent.orderId,                             
            currency: rallyEvent.cart.currency,                      
            items: createItems(rallyEvent.cart),
            ids: createProductIds(rallyEvent.cart),
            value: roundTo(rallyEvent.cart.total,3),
            payment_type: rallyEvent.cart.payment.type
            //discount
        }    
    };

    log('mads.purchase', eventData);
        
    dlPush({ microsoftads: null });  // Clear the previous googleads object.
    dlPush(eventData);
};

if (rallyEvent && rallyEvent.name === 'step' && rallyEvent.step) {
    switch(rallyEvent.step) {
        case 1:
            processStep1();
            break;
        case 2:
            processStep2();
            break;
        case 3:
            processStep3();
            break;
        case 4:
            processStep4();
            break;
    }
}

data.gtmOnSuccess();
